							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">NM, I a Genious!
<br />

<br />
Figured it out all by myself.  I let a monkey bang on the keyboard and randomly found the answer.
<br />

<br />
Here's what works for me...   
<br />

<br />
&lt;slash&gt;  &lt;colon&gt;  &lt;space&gt;  &lt;semicolon&gt;  &lt;space&gt;  &lt;command&gt;
<br />

<br />
Eg:
<br />

<br />
/: ; gsay I'm an Idiot, look at me ; useability Songwriter's Lobotomy
<br />

<br />
I can only find solice in the thought that there may be just one poor soul out there with eqally lacking skills that will save some embarrassment by not having to post to the entire EQ2 world their incompetence in the art of computing.   <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="Razz" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Happy Gaming
<br />

<br />
PS. Now if I can figure out how to 'pause' between commands, I'd be all set (for now)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
