<br />
*You can have 4 hotbars.  The first bar is accessible by just pressing the numbers 1-0 and also the - and = key.  The second bar is the same but hold down Shift.  The third bar uses Alt and the Fourth bar uses Ctrl
<br />

<br />
HotBar 3 spell 4 = Alt-4
<br />

<br />

