							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have 5 hotkey bars open at once.  3 of 'em can be hotkeyed and two are just for spells I don't use much.  However, just as with the multiple chat windows, there are bugs to be worked out.  Sometimes I end up with two secondary hotkeybars (both with alt+#) and sometimes they don't work at all.... but... I can usually get 'em to work by closing window and reopening them till i get 'em going.  
<br />

<br />
If you haven't tried it yet, I highly suggest seperating your chat windows into combat - others combat - chat -  game text.  The fact that you can make windows disappear when not in use makes this not such a cluttered design.<br />_________________<br />- Terras.  Swashbuckler on Lucan Dlere server.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
						</tr>
