							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Consider making a hotkey to /leavegroup.  I'm sure we've all had that new guy to the group arrive, with a train of critters behind him, only to die at your feet.  ... .... Thanks for the exp debt buddy..  Well, if you're getting chased while on your way to a group, the best thing to do is to leave the group until you shake your tail.   As long as you haven't actually initiated combat, leaving group should be no trouble.  So, hotkey it or remember it.... just don't give everyone else your debt <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />- Terras.  Swashbuckler on Lucan Dlere server.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
